/* Table: "C_DeductionFacility" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "C_DeductionFacility"
(
"FacilityID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"FacilityCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"FacilityName" NVARCHAR2(100),
"FacilityTypeID" NUMBER(32),
"MallID" NUMBER(32),
"BuildingID" NUMBER(32),
"FloorID" NUMBER(32),
"FireLength" DECIMAL(20, 4),
"FireWidth" DECIMAL(20, 4),
"FacilityArea" DECIMAL(20, 4),
"FacilityVectorInfo" VARCHAR2(4000),
"Enable" INTEGER,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
"ModifyBy" NUMBER(32),
"ModifyTime" TIMESTAMP,
"CADCode" VARCHAR2(20),
constraint PK_C_DEDUCTIONFACILITY primary key ("FacilityID")
);

comment on column "C_DeductionFacility"."Enable" is
'1：启用
0：停用';
